description:
Feature Description : User navigates to alert console page and creates the filters in advanced section and
      verifies all the results should be based on applied filters
name: Saved Filters

elements.name: Verifying the ITOps admin is able to save and apply the filter

steps.name: "admin" navigates to ust home page
"Admin" enters project name as "Automation_IB_16" in the search field
"admin" clicks on project name "Automation_IB_16"
"admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" enters source as "Solarwinds" and alert state as "Ticketed"
"admin" clicks on Save filter button
"admin" enters filter name as "IB" and Description as "Value 2"
"admin" clicks on save and apply button
"admin" verifies if "Filter saved successfully." message is displayed

elements.name: Verifying ITOps admin is able to apply the saved filter again

steps.name: "admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
"admin" Clicks on Saved Filter from advanced filter section "IB"
verify Apply and cancel buttons should be present
Verify the filter conditions are retrieved and click on Apply
verify Data shown should be based on the filter conditions "Solarwinds"

elements.name: Alert console UI should show all filter conditions as chips

steps.name: "admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on saved filters "IB"
"admin" verifies Remove all button is present
Chips should have a close button

elements.name: Verify user is able to remove all filter conditions via alert console once applied

steps.name: "admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on saved filters "IB"
"admin" clicks on Remove all link next to the chips displayed from Alert console
verify data should be reset to default set without any filter applied "Solarwinds"
verify All filter condition chips should be removed from UI

elements.name: Verify user is able to remove any filter conditions via alert console once applied

steps.name: "admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on saved filters "IB"
"admin" clicks on close button from any of the chip displayed
verify closed chips should not be displayed in UI
verify data should be reset to default set without any filter applied "Solarwinds"
"admin" clicks on Alerts page
"admin" clicks on advanced filter icon
verify all saved filters are displayed on left side "IB"
verify filter name, description and Created time should be displayed "IB", "Value 2", "08/5/2021 2:42:47 PM"
verify Expand button should be present for each saved filter
